body.p: During the past week, the following real-estate transfers took place in Chicago, in which either the buyer, the seller, or both were Scandinavians: H. Reiland to Hannah A. Nelson: Avenue M, north of 101st Street. Price, $1,500. A. Sundene to John L. Haverkampf: Central Park Avenue, north of Dunning Street. Price, $3,000. R. S. Olson to Andrew W. Anderson: Carpenter Street, south of Garfield Boulevard. Price, $1,050. G. Miller to Christina Lemde: Claremont Avenue, north of 69th Street. Price, $1,600. N. D. Arzner to Oliver A. Lindes: Parnell Avenue, north of 64th Street. Price, $2,600. C. H. Anderson to John M. LeClear: Lexington Street, west of South 40th Avenue. Price, $1,000.
